. quietly mestreg education njobs prestige i.female || birthyear: || id:, distribution(weibull) nohr

. stdmest Sm, reat(-.0921738 -2.028026) reatse(.2263078 .5722969) reatref(0.0 0.0) reatrefse(0.0 0.0) timevar(tv) contrast

